# 🐤 Floppy Bird Game

A responsive Flappy Bird–style browser game built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.  
The game works smoothly on both desktop and mobile devices with keyboard and touch controls.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Playable directly in the browser  
- Fully responsive (mobile + desktop support)  
- Keyboard (Spacebar) + Touch controls  
- Smooth gravity-based physics  
- Moving obstacle pipes  
- Live score tracking  
- Collision detection (pipes & ground)  
- Restart option after Game Over  
- High score saved using localStorage  
- Optional sound effects (jump, score, collision)  
- Increasing difficulty over time  

---

## 🎯 How to Play

### Desktop
Press **SPACEBAR** to make the bird jump.

### Mobile
Tap anywhere on the screen to jump.

### Objective
Pass through as many pipes as possible without hitting the pipes or the ground.  
Each successful pipe pass increases your score.

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- HTML5 – Structure  
- CSS3 – Styling & responsiveness  
- JavaScript (Vanilla JS) – Game logic & physics  
- HTML5 Canvas API – Rendering  

---

