---

## 📱 Mobile Optimization

- Uses `touchstart` event for tap controls  
- Prevents scrolling during gameplay  
- Responsive canvas scaling  
- Works on Android browsers, iOS Safari, and Chrome  

---

## ⚙️ Installation & Setup

1. Clone the repository:

   git clone https://github.com/your-username/floppy-bird.git  

2. Navigate to the project folder:

   cd floppy-bird  

3. Open `index.html` in your browser.

No additional dependencies required.

---

## 🧠 Game Logic Overview

- The bird has gravity applied every frame.  
- Pressing jump applies upward velocity.  
- Pipes spawn at intervals with random gap positions.  
- Collision detection checks bird vs pipes and bird vs ground.  
- Score increases when bird successfully passes a pipe.  
- Game states include Start, Playing, and Game Over.  

